Class XStream

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.io.InputStream
      • czlab.jasal.XStream
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Disposable, java.io.Closeable, java.lang.AutoCloseable

    public class XStream
extends java.io.InputStream
implements Disposable
    Wrapper on top of a File input stream such that it can delete itself from the file system when garbage collected.
